------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------+-------------+---------+--------------+--------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------
 test_copy_segmentby                      |                                                  |             |         |              |                    | 
 _timescaledb_internal._hyper_29_41_chunk | _timescaledb_internal.compress_hyper_30_42_chunk | {device_id} | {time}  | {t}          | {t}                | [{"type": "minmax", "column": "time", "source": "orderby"}]

SET timescaledb.enable_direct_compress_copy = true;
